  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, mix together sliced nectarines and granulated sugar.",
    "Transfer the nectarine mixture to a 9x9-inch baking dish.",
    "In another bowl, combine flour, oatmeal, brown sugar, and cinnamon.",
    "Add cold unsalted butter to the dry ingredients and mix until crumbly.",
